<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #B8860B; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    .price-breakdown { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Quotation Response</h1>
  <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
  <p>We have reviewed your quotation request (ID: {{quotationId}}).</p>
  
  <h2>Response Details:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Availability:</strong> {{response.availability}}</li>
    <li><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> {{response.estimatedDelivery}}</li>
    <li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> {{response.additionalNotes}}</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Price Breakdown:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Item Cost: {{response.priceBreakdown.itemCost}}</li>
    <li>Delivery Cost: {{response.priceBreakdown.deliveryCost}}</li>
    <li>Tax: {{response.priceBreakdown.tax}}</li>
    <li><strong>Total Cost:</strong> {{response.priceBreakdown.totalCost}}</li>
  </ul>

  <p>To proceed with your order, please log in to your account and accept the quotation.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>Car Grip Team</p>
</body>
</html> 